vote.title: Authorize (1) a Multiple Use Agreement with Texas Department of Transportation for the Southern Gateway Public Green located between South Marsalis Avenue and South Ewing Avenue to permit the City to construct, maintain, and operate a Public Green over Texas Department of Transportation right-of-way; and (2) execution of the Multiple Use Agreement including all terms, conditions, and documents required by the agreement - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
